snippet.title: ROCKETPODS - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
BUY NOW: 
https://firith.studio/rocketpods/

FIRITH STUDIO:
https://firith.studio

DISCORD: 
https://discordapp.com/invite/PfvQb42

Thrust your way through the galaxy's hardest obstacle courses! Learn how to control a RocketPod while also controlling your own frustration and fury. Start out as a novice, and leave as a Legend. Unlock the rarest RocketPods [collect 7 unique Pods], earn EXP, and attain new Rankings. Compare your pilot profile and mission results with your friends for competitive play!

Special Thanks to FloofyWoofles
